maps.name: A Community World
maps.description: A world map with 100k+ handpicked locations put together by over a hundred experienced players and map makers from the GeoGuessr community || More about ACW: https://bit.ly/acwmap || ACW discord: https://discord.gg/zausPpkFPM || The map contains only official Google Street View locations, meaning there should be no blurry images, photospheres or black screens in game

maps.name: A Skewed World
maps.description:
Welcome Bosnia & Cyprus! The original worst, best map. A Skewed World is designed to be played using the no moving, panning, or zooming (NMPZ) game mode. A Skewed World features 72,700 AI generated locations, with the camera positioning set +90/-90 (away from roads). Thousands of new locations are added monthly, the moment Google publishes them to keep the map up to date. Please report any unofficial/broken/unfair locations to username: @why_s on Discord.

Distribution: https://tinyurl.com/yc6x6fja

maps.name: A Tweaked World
maps.description:
Tired of world maps that spawn you on unpinpointable roads in the middle of nowhere? Try the first ever World Map, that is handpicked entirely and only for moving games. In theory you should get to info within 3' from spawn in at least one direction. The info might still be hard to use. Report too difficult, baity or generally bad locs via Discord: paschtetli
Distro: https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1jNu_kgC907i0tQxwvn_NQNkay1LYkPEE4j55UPa0H3o/edit?gid=1202995620#gid=1202995620

maps.name: A Varied World
maps.description: This map offers over 105,000 hand-picked locations from around the world. Only official coverage is included. The difficulty varies, you can encounter both places with signs and rounds with minimal information. A bit more info about the map and locations distribution list here (https://bit.ly/3KrxRPq).

maps.name: AI Generated World
maps.description:
The mother of all computer-generated maps, lightly seasoned with a touch of handpicked locations (~80/20) for spiciness.
  ~135k locations balanced between officially covered countries, depending on their coverage, surface area and landscape diversity. 
  The heading is slightly adjusted in order to avoid google car metas. 
 Distribution: https://tinyurl.com/ai-gen-world 
 Please report any unofficial/photosphere/impossible tunnel location at @rollinhill on discord.

maps.name: An Arbitrary Europe
maps.description: Explore Europe on this computer generated map spanning from Iceland and Portugal in the west all the way to the Ural mountains in the east. 104819 locations. See https://bit.ly/slashp for distribution and other maps.

maps.name: An Arbitrary Rural World
maps.description: Computer generated rural mix of An Arbitrary World and Dirty World. Please don't come complaining when a location doesn't fit your (non-computer) vision of rural :) 108338 locations. See https://bit.ly/slashp for distribution and other maps.

maps.name: An Arbitrary World
maps.description: Explore the world on this computer generated map with 110018 locations (only official Google coverage). NMPZ friendly. Great care has been taken to make the map balanced between countries as well as between subregions within countries. See https://bit.ly/slashp for distribution and other maps.

maps.name: Czech Republic
maps.description: This central European country with over 2000 castles was once was a hotspot of the Holy Roman Empire - the capital city of Prague was even home to the Holy Roman Emperor Charles IV! Even though Prague is a city full of historical sights, dont miss the kind of creepy Sedlec Ossuary, a bone church east of Prague. The chandelier is said to incorporate every human bone in the body at least once

maps.name: Czechia & Slovakia 50/50
maps.description:
30 000 locations in Czechia and 30 000 locations in Slovakia
Official Coverage Only | NMPZ Friendly
Locations may not always be pinpointable

maps.name: Dirty World
maps.description: Oh, dirt roads, how wonderful they are! There's just something about the rugged, unpaved paths that leads us to the unknown, the unexplored, and the untamed. The dust swirling up behind our vehicles, the stones that crunch beneath our feet, and the sensation of adventure that comes with each step! Dirt roads take us to remote and stunning places that we might never have known existed. They challenge us to push our limits, to discover what lies beyond the beaten path, and to embrace the beauty of the natural world. Whether we're walking, biking, or driving, there's something magical about the world's dirt roads that makes us feel alive and connected to the earth. So let's hit the road, let's embrace the dust, and let's explore the world's dirt roads to our hearts' content! 81681 locations. See https://bit.ly/slashp for distribution and other maps.

maps.name: Extreme Regionguessing
maps.description:
Inspired by the popular map 'Regionguessing' by Steve (https://www.geoguessr.com/maps/62e821d51775c653cc836849)
This map has 105000 locations spread across geoguessr's seven most covered countries (Russia, USA, Brazil, Canada, Australia, Indonesia and Mexico). Each country has 15000 locations. Intended to be played NM or NMPZ, Locations are AI generated and may not be pinpointable. Updated 11/09/2025

maps.name: Slovakia
maps.description: Located in one of the geographical midpoints of Europe (depending on how you count) Slovakia has more than 6000 caves and diverse nature. Visit the High Tatras mountains with glacier lakes and peaks at 2500 meters above sea level and mineral springs in one of many spa resorts.

maps.name: Terminus
maps.description:
~95k locations distributed at the edges of coverage, either being dead ends or places that are too remote for Google drivers (may also contain locations where the coverage is inconsistent).
  Pretty high probability to find unconventional and interesting spots.
 Some locations might be skewed NMPZ.
  Distribution: https://tinyurl.com/t3rminus
